	<div class="col-xs-12 contenedor-mapa-parrilla pdg-lr0">
		<div class="contenedor-mapa open no_fixed">
			<div class="btn-cerrar-mapa shadow-btn-map">
				<!--<img src="/css/img/parrillas/icon-close-map.png">-->
				<span class="icon-anterior"></span>
			</div>
			<div id="contenedor-mapa" class="area-mapa">
			</div>
			<script type="text/javascript" src="/js/leaflet.js"></script>
			<script type="text/javascript">
				
				var alto_total = $( window ).height() - $('.navbar-fixed-top').height();
				$('.contenedor-mapa').css('height', alto_total+'px');
				
			</script>

			<script type="text/javascript">
				
				var protocol = location.protocol !== "https:" ? "http:\/\/" : "https:\/\/";
				var osmUrl = protocol + '{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png',
				osmAttrib = '&copy; <a href="{$WEB_PROTOCOL}openstreetmap.org/copyright">OpenStreetMap</a> contributors',
				osm = L.tileLayer(osmUrl, {maxZoom: 18, attribution: osmAttrib});
				
				var map;	
				var ubications = [];
				var locations = [];
				var infobox = [];
				var allMyMarkers = [];
				locations = [
				
								
					[40.3460876,-1.1077903,'537879','h632072','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3456879,-1.1064345,'134661','h126055','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3296868,-1.1059549,'318844','h422364','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3466719,-1.1081084,'546676','h637567','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3466719,-1.1081084,'546676','h639313','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3389154,-1.104834,'416952','h558516','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3389206,-1.1048335,'301040','h385491','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3485457,-1.111777,'515589','h618639','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3420081,-1.1067998999999,'563801','h651201','0','0'],
				
								
					[40.3420081,-1.1067998999999,'563801','h651200','0','0'],
				
								
				];

				function initialize() {
					var lat = 40.343834;
					var lng = -1.107522;
					var zoom = 15;

					if (map != undefined) { map.remove(); allMyMarkers = []; }
					
					map = L.map('contenedor-mapa', {
						center: L.latLng(lat, lng),
						zoom: zoom,
						zoomControl: false,
						dragging: false,
						boxZoom: false, 
						scrollWheelZoom: false,
						doubleClickZoom: false
					}).addLayer(osm);
					
					var bounds = new L.LatLngBounds();
					
					for (i = 0; i < locations.length; i++) {
						if (locations[i][5] == '0'){
							icono = '/css/img/parrillas/puntero.png'
						} else {
							icono = '/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png'
						}
						var myIcon = L.icon({
							iconUrl: icono,
							iconSize: [33, 41]
						});
						var marker = L.marker([locations[i][0], locations[i][1]], {icon: myIcon} ).addTo(map);
						bounds.extend(marker.getLatLng());

						marker.on('mouseover', (function(marker, i, e) {
							return function(){
								var icon = L.icon({
									iconUrl: "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_activo.png",
									iconSize: [33, 41]
								});
								marker.setIcon(icon);
								destacaVivienda(locations[i][2]);
							}
						})(marker, i));

						marker.on('mouseout', (function(marker, i, e) {
							return function(){
								var pathIcon;
								if (locations[i][4] == '1'){
									pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_activo.png";
								} else {
									if (locations[i][5] == '1'){
										pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png";
									} else {
										pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero.png";
									}
								}

								marker.setIcon(L.icon({
									iconUrl: pathIcon,
									iconSize: [33, 41]
								}));
								noDestacaVivienda(locations[i][2]);
							}
						})(marker, i));

						var titulo = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .localizacion-map').text();
						var tipo = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .texto-tipo-mapa').text();
						var img = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .img-map').attr('src');
						var url = $('#'+locations[i][3]).data("url");
						var fav_status;
						if ($('#'+locations[i][3]+' .fav-icon').hasClass('on')) fav_status = 'on';
						else fav_status = 'off';
						var id_perfil = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .fav-icon').data("id-perfil");
						var id_anuncio = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .fav-icon').data("id-anuncio");
						var fav_tipo = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .fav-icon').data("type");
						var precio = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .contenedor-precio').text();
						var caract = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .contenedor-caracteristicas').html();
						var num_img = $('#'+locations[i][3]+' .contador-imagenes').text();
						var contenido = "<div class='ficha_map'>"+
											"<a href='"+url+"'>"+
												"<span class='titulo'>"+titulo+"</span>"+
											"</a>"+
											
												"<div class='imagen'>"+
													"<div id='favico_map_"+id_anuncio+"' class='fav-icon "+fav_status+"' onclick=\"addfavirito('"+id_perfil+"','"+id_anuncio+"','"+fav_tipo+"',1)\"></div>"+
													"<a href='"+url+"'>"+
														"<div class='contenedor-destacado-tipo'>"+
															"<span class='texto-tipo'>"+tipo+"</span>"+
														"</div>"+
														"<img src='"+img+"' class='img-responsive'>"+
														"<div class='contenedor-contador-imagenes'>"+
															"<span class='contador-imagenes'>"+num_img+"</span>"+
														"</div>"+
														"<div class='contenedor-precio'>"+
															"<span class='cont-precio'>"+precio+"</span>"+
														"</div>"+
													"</a>"+
												"</div>"+
											"<div class='caract'>"+
											caract+
											"</div>"+
											"<div class='con-btn'>"+
												"<a onclick=\"javascript:contacto_parrilla('"+locations[i][3]+"')\" class='btn-contactar br3 tr05'>"+
													"<span class='txt-content'>"+
														"<span class='icon-mail'></span>"+
														"Contactar"+
													"</span>"+
												"</a>"+
											"</div>"+
										"</div>";
						marker.bindPopup(contenido, {
								closeButton: false,
								maxWidth: 256,
								offset: L.point(0, -10)
						});		

						marker.on('click', (function(marker, i, e) {
							return function() {
								for (t = 0; t < locations.length; t++) {
									if (locations[t][4] == '1'){
										locations[t][4] = '0';
										locations[t][5] = '1';
										var icon = L.icon({
											iconUrl: "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png",
											iconSize: [33, 41]
										});
										allMyMarkers[t].setIcon(icon);
									} else {
										var pathIcon;
										if (locations[i][5] == '1'){
											pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png";
										} else {
											pathIcon ="/css/img/parrillas/puntero.png";
										}
										marker.setIcon(L.icon({
												iconUrl: pathIcon,
												iconSize: [33, 41]
												})
											);
									}
								}
								locations[i][4] = '1';

								marker.setIcon(L.icon({
									iconUrl: "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_activo.png",
									iconSize: [33, 41]
									})
								);
							}
						})(marker, i));

						allMyMarkers.push( marker )		
					}

					map.on('click', (function(e) {
						for (t = 0; t < locations.length; t++) {
							var pathIcon;
							if (locations[t][4] == '1'){
								locations[t][4] = '0';
								locations[t][5] = '1';
								pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png";
							} else {
								locations[t][4] = '0';
								if (locations[t][5] == 1){
									pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png";
								} else {
									pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero.png";
								}
							}
							allMyMarkers[t].setIcon(L.icon({
								iconUrl: pathIcon,
								iconSize: [33, 41]
								})
							);
							allMyMarkers[t].setZIndexOffset(300);
						}
					}));

					map.fitBounds(bounds.pad(0.2))
    			}

				function destacaVivienda(id_vivienda){
					$('.contenedor-parrilla-inmuebles').find('.'+id_vivienda+'').addClass('overmap');
				}

				function noDestacaVivienda(id_vivienda){
					$('.contenedor-parrilla-inmuebles').find('.'+id_vivienda+'').removeClass('overmap');
				}

				function destacamarker(id_marker, id_vivienda) {
					allMyMarkers[id_marker].setIcon(L.icon({
							iconUrl: "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_activo.png",
							iconSize: [33, 41]
						})
					);
					allMyMarkers[id_marker].setZIndexOffset(500);
				}

				function normalizamarker(id_marker,id_vivienda) {
					var pathIcon;
					if  (locations[id_marker][3] == id_vivienda){
						if  (locations[id_marker][4] == '1'){
							pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_activo.png";
						} else {
							if  (locations[id_marker][5] == '1'){
								pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero_visitado.png";
							} else {
								pathIcon = "/css/img/parrillas/puntero.png";
							}
						}

						allMyMarkers[id_marker].setIcon(L.icon({
								iconUrl: pathIcon,
								iconSize: [33, 41]
							}
						));
						allMyMarkers[id_marker].setZIndexOffset(300);
					}
				}

				$(document).ready(function() {
					initialize();
				});
			
			</script>
